data.description: Join us for an exclusive Open House this Saturday, February 3rd, from 1 pm to 3 pm, and step into the epitome of modern living with this beautifully crafted single-family home built in 2022. Nestled on three finished levels, this residence boasts a 3-car garage and a fully fenced-in backyard, providing both convenience and privacy. The meticulously designed floor plan by DR Horton includes a main-level bedroom and office, catering to the demands of today's lifestyle. The kitchen is equipped with stainless steel appliances, complemented by granite countertops and high-end Luxury Vinyl Plank (LVP) flooring throughout.  As you ascend to the upper level, discover three spacious bedrooms, a laundry room, and a generously sized recreation room, perfect for entertainment. The primary bathroom on this level stands out with its luxurious fixtures, adding a touch of elegance to the space. The fully finished walk-out basement offers additional living space, complete with a full bathroom and an extra bedroom, providing flexibility for guests or extended family.  This home is not only aesthetically pleasing but also environmentally conscious, featuring solar panels for sustainable living. Impeccable craftsmanship and thoughtful details make this property a true gem. Don't miss the chance to make this dream home yours. Schedule your appointment today to explore the exceptional features and functionality that this property has to offer. Contact us for more details and to secure your private showing. We look forward to welcoming you to your future home!
